title: Nine Inch Nails: To Become A Virus [an ets fan remix album]
description:
A Nine Inch Nails fan single in an echoingthesound.org project. To Become A Virus is a compilation of fan remixes of The Warning, Vessel, and The Greater Good collected together by M J McLean [ets username mjmclean]. The tracks have been selected from hundreds as interesting, unique, or just plain incredible mixes of the title song.

Full artwork is provided in this download, and it is at 300 dpi for all your printing needs.

01 The Warning [Futurism Mix] by nuclearlogic
02 The Warning [The Sign] by NightBender
03 The Warning [Nth Mix] by NthWhtk
04 The Warning [Pellucid Psychogenic Squall Mix] by M J McLean
05 Vessel [Twilight Mix] by Erasemoi
06 The Greater Good [Faithful To The End] by Dvittet vs INC
07 The Warning [Messenger] by tyhrsn
08 The Warning [Wiped Clean] by TweakerRay
09 Vessel [Never Alone] by Janek Leskiewicz

Total time: 39:34
